<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>IMPORTANT: Your Appointment Reminder</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f5f7fa;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            color: #333;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 20px auto;
            background: white;
            border-radius: 10px;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        .header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #4a6fa5 0%, #2c3e50 100%);
            padding: 25px;
            text-align: center;
            color: white;
            position: relative;
        }

        .header::after {
            content: "IMPORTANT REMINDER";
            position: absolute;
            bottom: -10px;
            left: 50%;
            transform: translateX(-50%);
            background: #e74c3c;
            color: white;
            padding: 5px 15px;
            border-radius: 20px;
            font-size: 12px;
            font-weight: bold;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
        }

        .logo {
            height: 50px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .church-name {
            font-size: 22px;
            font-weight: 700;
            margin: 5px 0;
            letter-spacing: 0.5px;
        }

        .content {
            padding: 30px;
        }

        h1 {
            color: #e74c3c;
            font-size: 24px;
            margin-top: 0;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .urgent-banner {
            background: #fff8e6;
            border: 2px dashed #e74c3c;
            padding: 15px;
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 25px;
            border-radius: 5px;
        }

        .reminder-box {
            background: #f8f9fa;
            border-left: 4px solid #e74c3c;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 25px 0;
            border-radius: 0 5px 5px 0;
            position: relative;
        }

        .reminder-box::before {
            content: "‚è∞";
            position: absolute;
            left: -30px;
            top: 50%;
            transform: translateY(-50%);
            font-size: 24px;
            background: white;
            width: 40px;
            height: 40px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        .detail-row {
            margin-bottom: 12px;
            display: flex;
        }

        .detail-label {
            font-weight: 600;
            min-width: 120px;
            color: #4a6fa5;
        }

        .timezone-note {
            background: #e8f4fc;
            padding: 10px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin-top: 15px;
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #2c3e50;
        }

        .action-buttons {
            margin: 25px 0;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .btn {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 12px 25px;
            background: #4a6fa5;
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin: 0 10px;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }

        .btn:hover {
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            box-shadow: 0 5px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        .btn-outline {
            background: transparent;
            border: 2px solid #4a6fa5;
            color: #4a6fa5;
        }

        .btn-urgent {
            background: #e74c3c;
            border-color: #e74c3c;
        }

        .footer {
            background: #2c3e50;
            color: white;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 13px;
        }

        .footer a {
            color: #a3c4ff;
            text-decoration: none;
        }

        .location {
            margin-top: 15px;
            padding-top: 15px;
            border-top: 1px dashed #ddd;
        }

        .countdown {
            text-align: center;
            margin: 20px 0;
            font-size: 18px;
            color: #e74c3c;
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        @media only screen and (max-width: 600px) {
            .container {
                margin: 0;
                border-radius: 0;
            }

            .btn {
                display: block;
                margin: 10px 0;
            }

            .detail-row {
                flex-direction: column;
            }

            .detail-label {
                margin-bottom: 5px;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <img src="/source//public/fg-logo.jpg" alt="Church Logo" class="logo">
            <div class="church-name">Ethiopian Full Gospel Believers Church <br>
                (Silver Spring Local)
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="content">
            <h1>YOUR APPOINTMENT IS COMING SOON!</h1>

            <div class="urgent-banner">
                <strong>‚è≥ Don't forget!</strong> Your appointment is scheduled for <strong>
                    <%= preferredDate %> at <%= preferredTime %>
                </strong> (<%= timeDifference %>).
            </div>

            <p>Dear <strong>
                    <%= fullName %>
                </strong>,</p>

            <p>We're excited to meet with you! This is your official reminder about your upcoming appointment. Please
                review the details below carefully:</p>

            <div class="reminder-box">
                <div class="detail-row">
                    <div class="detail-label">Date:</div>
                    <div><strong>
                            <%= preferredDate %>
                        </strong></div>
                </div>
                <div class="detail-row">
                    <div class="detail-label">Time:</div>
                    <div><strong>
                            <%= preferredTime %>
                        </strong> (Your local time)</div>
                </div>
                <div class="detail-row">
                    <div class="detail-label">New York Time:</div>
                    <div>
                        <%= newYorkTime %> on <%= newYorkDate %>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="detail-row">
                    <div class="detail-label">Meeting Type:</div>
                    <div><strong>
                            <%= medium==='in-person' ? 'In-Person Meeting' : 'Online Meeting' %>
                        </strong></div>
                </div>

                <div class="timezone-note">
                    <strong>Note:</strong> Our church operates on Eastern Time (New York). The time difference is <%=
                        timeDifference %>.
                </div>

                <% if (medium==='in-person' ) { %>
                    <div class="location">
                        <div class="detail-row">
                            <div class="detail-label">Location:</div>
                            <div><strong>Ethiopian Full Gospel Believers Church</strong><br>
                                914 Silver Spring Ave, Suite 204 B, Silver Spring, MD 20910, USA<br>
                                (Main Office, Room 201)</div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="detail-row">
                            <div class="detail-label">Parking:</div>
                            <div>Visitor parking available in the west lot</div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="detail-row">
                            <div class="detail-label">What to bring:</div>
                            <div>Please bring any necessary documents and a photo ID</div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <% } else { %>
                        <div class="location">
                            <div class="detail-row">
                                <div class="detail-label">Meeting Link:</div>
                                <div><a href="<%= meetingLink || '#' %>"
                                        style="color: #4a6fa5; font-weight: bold;">Click to join online meeting</a>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="detail-row">
                                <div class="detail-label">Instructions:</div>
                                <div>
                                    <ul style="margin-top: 5px; padding-left: 20px;">
                                        <li>Please join 5-10 minutes early to test your connection</li>
                                        <li>Use headphones for better audio quality</li>
                                        <li>Ensure good lighting so we can see you clearly</li>
                                    </ul>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <% } %>
            </div>

            <div class="countdown">
                ‚è∞ Only 1 day until your appointment!
            </div>

            <div class="action-buttons">
                <a href="<%= rescheduleLink || '#' %>" class="btn btn-outline">üìÖ Reschedule Appointment</a>
                <a href="<%= cancelLink || '#' %>" class="btn btn-outline">‚ùå Cancel Appointment</a>
                <% if (medium !=='in-person' ) { %>
                    <a href="<%= meetingLink || '#' %>" class="btn btn-urgent">üöÄ Join Meeting Now (when time comes)</a>
                    <% } %>
            </div>

            <p style="margin-top: 30px;"><strong>Important Notes:</strong></p>
            <ul style="margin-top: 5px; padding-left: 20px;">
                <li>Please arrive/join 5-10 minutes early</li>
                <li>Late arrivals may need to be rescheduled</li>
                <li>If you need to cancel, please do so at least 24 hours in advance</li>
                <li>For emergencies, call (240) 821-0361</li>
            </ul>

            <p>We're praying for you and look forward to our time together!</p>

            <p>Blessings,<br>
                <strong>The Pastoral Care Team</strong><br>
                Ethiopian Full Gospel Believers Church<br>
                (Silver Spring Local)
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="footer">
            <div style="margin-bottom: 10px;">
                Ethiopian Full Gospel Believers Church (Silver Spring Local)<br>
                914 Silver Spring Ave, Suite 204 B, Silver Spring, MD 20910, USA
            </div>
            <div>
                <a href="mailto:office@efgbcssl.org">office@efgbcssl.org</a> |
                <a href="tel:+12408210361">(240) 821-0361</a> |
                <a href="https://efgbcssl.org">efgbcssl.org</a>
            </div>
            <div style="margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12px;">
                You're receiving this email because you have an upcoming appointment.
                <% if (unsubscribeLink) { %>
                    <a href="<%= unsubscribeLink %>" style="color: #a3c4ff;">Unsubscribe from reminders</a>
                    <% } %>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>

</html>